ed="T" n="0892c26"/><persName key="A008831">釋慧演</persName>，姓苗氏，<placeName key="PL000000027119">襄陽</placeName>人也。父為東平紏曹。<lb
ed="T" n="0892c27"/><persName key="A008831">演</persName>幼入開元寺<!--找不到此地-->，聞經歡喜，求於<persName key="A013896">辯章法師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0892c28"/>所度脫。<persName key="A013896">章</persName>日講涅槃經，<persName key="A008831">演</persName>常隨聽入神。既<lb
ed="T" n="0892c29"/>通深義，復能講談。一日結侶同遊<placeName key="PL000000043316">華下</placeName>，思<pb ed="T" n="0893a" xml:id="T50.2061.0893a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0893a01"/>登毛女峯<!--找不到此地-->，觀仙掌，路出<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛中</placeName>，乃參<persName key="A005612">荷澤祖<lb
ed="T" n="0893a02"/>師</persName>，通達大觀。因入<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>，遂住<placeName key="PL000000029560">澧陽</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000000197">江南</placeName>得<lb
ed="T" n="0893a03"/>道者多矣。<date key="j19617861961814" notAfter-iso="+0659-03-01" notBefore-iso="+0659-02-01"><name>貞元</name>十二年</date>終，享齡七十九云。</p>
